Former Minister of Information, Professor Jerry Gana, has rejoined the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP). Gana joined the PDP from the Social Democratic Party (SDP) alongside some of his supporters. In the reception to mark his return in Bida, Gana pledged to work for the interest of the party, declaring that he and his supporters were back for good. Gana stated the country needs help as a lot of sectors of the economy are nosediving. In March 2018, Jerry Gana, who was a member of the Board of Trustees of the PDP, ditched the party for the SDP.